{"tid":175133,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"關西13日賞櫻之旅","createTime":"2017-03-27T09:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T05:35:08.000Z","uid":86810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37d63ab36b6b7c46628fc53a2e466faa61ba7776","tid":175133,"uid":86810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"30號出發，去程同回程都係下就2點左右，第一次去日本乜都唔識，雖然已經狂爬文做功課，但唔知要買咩pass，請各日本通指點，同求睇下以下行程有冇問題<br />\n<br />\n（住京都）第一日：關空-&gt;京都<br />\n（住京都）第二日：河原町-&gt;烏丸通-&gt;鴨川-&gt;金閣寺<br />\n（住京都）第三日：岡本和服(已book)-&gt;清水寺-&gt;八坂神社-&gt;祗園-&gt;花見小路-&gt;哲學之道-&gt;伏見稻荷<br />\n（住京都）第四日：嵐山嵯-&gt;峨峨野<br />\n（住京都）第五日：奈良<br />\n（住大阪）第六日：京都-&gt;大阪-&gt;心齋橋-&gt;道頓堀-&gt;黑門市場-&gt;難波<br />\n（住大阪）第七日：姬路-&gt;神戶<br />\n（住大阪）第八日：環球影城(已book)<br />\n（住大阪）第九日：大阪城-&gt;公園梅田<br />\n（住大阪）第十日：未諗到<br />\n（住白濱）第十一日：大阪-&gt;白濱-&gt;白濱景點<br />\n（住白濱）第十二日：白濱景點-&gt;臨空outlet<br />\n第十三日：白濱-&gt;關空<br />\n<br />\n好期待做好日本既野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce74d6a223676fd43cb082b96a89cabeab077aa","tid":175133,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:44:47.000Z","msg":"4月3出發，打算用八達通算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d056a40535fa944d9e1f2f534c937d2550859cd","tid":175133,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:45:50.000Z","msg":"第三日一定唔夠時間<br />\n除非你去伏見影完相就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1283f64e2253727b6892d8af63acdaa560cb02e","tid":175133,"uid":86810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:00:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第三日一定唔夠時間<br />\n除非你去伏見影完相就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有個和服心，想著和服去伏見個鳥居影相，如果將哲學之道改另一日會唔會好啲？或者將清水寺改成夜晚去？"},{"pid":"d675cd16a782d6be7e6421bc68376b6e78895abf","tid":175133,"uid":98671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:07:06.000Z","msg":"一路順風<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451596bc18d353ff538b76ae7c6b9dd027f9366f","tid":175133,"uid":86810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4月3出發，打算用八達通算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我澳門直去香港機場上機，用唔著八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cef05ed18f034373068a9dbd49492e03ce4432","tid":175133,"uid":22150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:31:09.000Z","msg":"清水寺維修緊"},{"pid":"5a61ffc2f9ee1525c7ba6491f2ff7f2819c32605","tid":175133,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4月3出發，打算用八達通算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我澳門直去香港機場上機，用唔著八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢叫你一張icoca搞掂"},{"pid":"3118556e40ee252f65ea28c629b4dba663c0ce0e","tid":175133,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清水寺維修緊</blockquote><br />\n個舞台封左姐"},{"pid":"2eb13b5e0781f50379e15a25ef8bf9c938ce1774","tid":175133,"uid":86810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>4月3出發，打算用八達通算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我澳門直去香港機場上機，用唔著八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢叫你一張icoca搞掂</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可唔可以請問一下關西周遊卡岩唔岩我用？"},{"pid":"2ecdee3b9c2ed8dc158bd82819caef5ef7b69e35","tid":175133,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"第三日咁既行程一定唔夠時間，除非你踩單車，或者千本居居唔諗住行哂同影少少就走<br />\n搭巴士都唔夠時間，除非你果日好好彩，一到巴士站就有你要搭既車"},{"pid":"da21ee2102136968de832ac296542b4a95c7d70e","tid":175133,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>4月3出發，打算用八達通算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我澳門直去香港機場上機，用唔著八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢叫你一張icoca搞掂</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可唔可以請問一下關西周遊卡岩唔岩我用？</blockquote><br />\n岩，不過用唔到來回白濱"},{"pid":"95dcd38d1e88fcd832f61a2560826f2f54acbf5c","tid":175133,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:51:15.000Z","msg":"依家既清水寺<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/195113_5cb26f0cda8083fc036999e37a279e87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F195113_5cb26f0cda8083fc036999e37a279e87.jpg&h=6dde9e60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db569973312bd59d18e2ee6fa1b951ac02d77357","tid":175133,"uid":86810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家既清水寺<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/195113_5cb26f0cda8083fc036999e37a279e87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F195113_5cb26f0cda8083fc036999e37a279e87.jpg&h=6dde9e60&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪淨係得清水舞台整緊，其他地方唔知有冇整緊，定係清水寺淨係得依個舞台值得睇？<br />\n<br />\n我見有post話33間堂值得去，等我加埋入行程先"},{"pid":"dfdef4a0ac38a495c9284ae3e3731e8e9821af8d","tid":175133,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家既清水寺<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/195113_5cb26f0cda8083fc036999e37a279e87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F195113_5cb26f0cda8083fc036999e37a279e87.jpg&h=6dde9e60&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪淨係得清水舞台整緊，其他地方唔知有冇整緊，定係清水寺淨係得依個舞台值得睇？<br />\n<br />\n我見有post話33間堂值得去，等我加埋入行程先</blockquote><br />\n依家係...<br />\n其實日本寺廟咁多人去係因為個個寺都有櫻花可以影，未去過既咪去下囉，清水寺入面有兩舊姻緣石，所以都多日本妹去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s4Ss516.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs4Ss516.jpg&h=dc67dee6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/210826_46b8375eb85b9a736caae8ccef68cf49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F210826_46b8375eb85b9a736caae8ccef68cf49.jpg&h=36e37d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TL6CAM0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTL6CAM0.jpg&h=23f8efb7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/210831_37b6016a139f0c2a05afd3a75b3252fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F210831_37b6016a139f0c2a05afd3a75b3252fe.jpg&h=e91b8359&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ea1d6d2986a0e9f1c7f828e8bda8625f6842648","tid":175133,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>4月3出發，打算用八達通算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我澳門直去香港機場上機，用唔著八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢叫你一張icoca搞掂</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可唔可以請問一下關西周遊卡岩唔岩我用？</blockquote><br />\n我懶，唔係差一千幾百就算9數"},{"pid":"400e16e9a53d4371a8331be85c57c6e6850f61ad","tid":175133,"uid":86810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:44:51.000Z","msg":"有冇人話我知京都依家係咪一粒櫻花都未開？"},{"pid":"24706f9fd1fb6b40da1389b5f08946f23b1e289e","tid":175133,"uid":47775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"我幾日去過 淨係見到一兩顆開左<br />\n預計4月1左右開"},{"pid":"361e51a30b9d08858bd29955cae67cbec22a9f54","tid":175133,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:31:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人話我知京都依家係咪一粒櫻花都未開？</blockquote><br />\n點都有一兩棵開咗既，唔好諗住好靚<br />\n東京都未開呀"},{"pid":"2e2480ae484c4fcb9c45ef277a69d7f84f3647e4","tid":175133,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:58:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1884fd0c94152f4d91a6044a1010d8331d80e088","tid":175133,"uid":90987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:01:35.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6360cc62f927a6e5a0bf23ca06a299c385fb0028","tid":175133,"uid":15659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:04:13.000Z","msg":"白濱同關西空港距離好遠㗎，第十二日不如住和歌山市"},{"pid":"7b1786389506e1da0d07e92f7bf902b3e804309f","tid":175133,"uid":53399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第三日一定唔夠時間<br />\n除非你去伏見影完相就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有個和服心，想著和服去伏見個鳥居影相，如果將哲學之道改另一日會唔會好啲？或者將清水寺改成夜晚去？</blockquote><br />\n伏見稻荷一入夜你係咩都影唔到"},{"pid":"40a87eb84c4f4a77cf7f4baa0dc80c06a2c738c9","tid":175133,"uid":28560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:05:29.000Z","msg":"京都賞櫻唔去醍醐寺同平安神宮神苑?"},{"pid":"b7d361207b8f77d39b95047e076ef88442b46e2f","tid":175133,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:38:01.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}